ww.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span>, tied for third!!</li> </ol> <p>The final tallies, winners, and Judges' Awards will be going up within the next day! Stay tuned!</p> 
